    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-11-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-11-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="314" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d314">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Eustis</persName> to
                                    Mr. <persName type="to">Olney</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-11-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 22,
                                        1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Just received Waller’s reply. It is as follows: “Maintain my right of
                                claim for indemnity. Have written.” Signed, Waller.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Eustis</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
